00:21:25.120 --> 00:21:27.670 align:middle line:90%
And I said, how's the stress?

00:21:27.670 --> 00:21:29.920 align:middle line:84%
Because he'd told me
he was very stressed.

00:21:29.920 --> 00:21:32.300 align:middle line:84%
And he ran a chain of
small supermarkets,

00:21:32.300 --> 00:21:33.520 align:middle line:90%
and I'm always stressed.

00:21:33.520 --> 00:21:34.900 align:middle line:90%
He said, what stress?

00:21:34.900 --> 00:21:37.060 align:middle line:90%
I don't have any stress.

00:21:37.060 --> 00:21:41.410 align:middle line:84%
Simply by changing his diet,
no stress, more energy,

00:21:41.410 --> 00:21:43.840 align:middle line:84%
energy to exercise,
which is very

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:50.290 align:middle line:84%
important, same job, same
mortgage, same wife, no stress.

00:21:50.290 --> 00:21:54.550 align:middle line:84%
The point is, when you get what
you put into your body right,

00:21:54.550 --> 00:21:55.870 align:middle line:90%
