Sometimes people say to me,
but if you take vitamins,

00:22:10.960 --> 00:22:12.820 align:middle line:84%
aren't you just making
expensive urine?

00:22:12.820 --> 00:22:16.120 align:middle line:90%


00:22:16.120 --> 00:22:20.740 align:middle line:84%
