when you drink water?

00:22:24.170 --> 00:22:27.250 align:middle line:90%
Yep, you pee it out.

00:22:27.250 --> 00:22:31.130 align:middle line:84%
So does that mean I
shouldn't drink water?

00:22:31.130 --> 00:22:31.930 align:middle line:90%
The answer is no.

00:22:31.930 --> 00:22:33.933 align:middle line:84%
Of course you need
to drink water.

00:22:33.933 --> 00:22:35.350 align:middle line:84%
And an important
point about water

00:22:35.350 --> 00:22:37.480 align:middle line:84%
is what happens
between you drinking

