unless you've got
patented, that is,

00:31:16.310 --> 00:31:22.140 align:middle line:84%
a man made product
that only you can sell.

00:31:22.140 --> 00:31:28.550 align:middle line:84%
And for that simple reason, we
are now stuck firmly in an era

00:31:28.550 --> 00:31:33.440 align:middle line:84%
