where you feel connected,
you really feel full of life,

00:35:11.120 --> 00:35:15.770 align:middle line:84%
and I meet so few people
who have that experience.

00:35:15.770 --> 00:35:18.470 align:middle line:84%
So my work in the
field of nutrition

00:35:18.470 --> 00:35:24.950 align:middle line:84%
is not only to help people like
you recover happiness, recover

00:35:24.950 --> 00:35:28.460 align:middle line:84%
health, and become
free of pain but also

00:35:28.460 --> 00:35:34.910 align:middle line:84%
to discover that there is a
whole level of energy that

00:35:34.910 --> 00:35:38.600 align:middle line:84%
is available to you
right now, and all

00:35:38.600 --> 00:35:42.170 align:middle line:84%
you have to do is make
very simple changes,

00:35:42.170 --> 00:35:45.650 align:middle line:84%
get your nutrition right,
get your lifestyle right,

00:35:45.650 --> 00:35:48.740 align:middle line:84%
and all of that will
be available to you.

00:35:48.740 --> 00:35:54.520 align:middle line:84%
All of my work is about helping
people to have that experience.

00:35:54.520 --> 00:35:58.330 align:middle line:84%
And believe me, once you've had
that, your old habits will just

00:35:58.330 --> 00:35:59.130 align:middle line:90%
fall away.

00:35:59.130 --> 00:36:02.350 align:middle line:90%


00:36:02.350 --> 00:36:06.490 align:middle line:84%
I'm often asked, what
is the real problem?

00:36:06.490 --> 00:36:09.190 align:middle line:84%
I mean, how have we
got into the place

00:36:09.190 --> 00:36:13.270 align:middle line:84%
that we're at with all these
diseases in the 21st century

00:36:13.270 --> 00:36:17.650 align:middle line:84%
and stress and tired
and depressed and so on?

00:36:17.650 --> 00:36:22.390 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's really
a lack of connection.

00:36:22.390 --> 00:36:27.580 align:middle line:84%
In some communities where
they grow their own food

00:36:27.580 --> 00:36:31.000 align:middle line:84%
and are more socially connected,
people are much happier.

00:36:31.000 --> 00:36:34.210 align:middle line:84%
These are sometimes
poorer communities.

00:36:34.210 --> 00:36:36.870 align:middle line:84%
And yet, there's some
kind of connection.

00:36:36.870 --> 00:36:38.710 align:middle line:84%
And I think we've
lost that connection

00:36:38.710 --> 00:36:44.980 align:middle line:84%
with this striving towards
our high technology existence.

00:36:44.980 --> 00:36:48.050 align:middle line:84%
With texting and emails
and computers and so on,

00:36:48.050 --> 00:36:54.220 align:middle line:84%
somehow we lose that ability to
just connect with someone else.

00:36:54.220 --> 00:36:56.890 align:middle line:84%
And also to really
connect with ourselves,

00:36:56.890 --> 00:37:01.060 align:middle line:84%
to be comfortable
in being yourself.

00:37:01.060 --> 00:37:03.550 align:middle line:90%
And also to connect with food.

00:37:03.550 --> 00:37:06.310 align:middle line:84%
You can eat now without
really ever knowing

00:37:06.310 --> 00:37:08.860 align:middle line:84%
that the food comes
from the ground.

00:37:08.860 --> 00:37:10.990 align:middle line:84%
So when we work with
kids in schools,

00:37:10.990 --> 00:37:14.980 align:middle line:84%
we always make sure that they
grow some of their own food

00:37:14.980 --> 00:37:17.320 align:middle line:84%
and see it from a
seed to the food,

00:37:17.320 --> 00:37:21.340 align:middle line:84%
because when you make a salad
or you make dinner out of food

00:37:21.340 --> 00:37:24.730 align:middle line:84%
that you've grown
yourself in the earth,

00:37:24.730 --> 00:37:27.040 align:middle line:84%
it's a whole
different experience.

00:37:27.040 --> 00:37:31.270 align:middle line:84%
Our body is literally
made from the elements.

00:37:31.270 --> 00:37:35.350 align:middle line:84%
And in due course, we will
go back to the elements.

00:37:35.350 --> 00:37:38.560 align:middle line:84%
So nutrition isn't just
this kind of dry thing

00:37:38.560 --> 00:37:40.490 align:middle line:84%
that you have to
do to be healthy.

00:37:40.490 --> 00:37:42.760 align:middle line:90%
It's absolutely fundamental.

00:37:42.760 --> 00:37:45.550 align:middle line:84%
You are literally made
from what you eat.

00:37:45.550 --> 00:37:47.455 align:middle line:84%
And if you can get
involved in your nutrition

00:37:47.455 --> 00:37:51.610 align:middle line:84%
and enjoy what you buy
and enjoy preparing food

00:37:51.610 --> 00:37:54.730 align:middle line:84%
and enjoy eating it,
then you can start

00:37:54.730 --> 00:37:56.830 align:middle line:90%
to regain that connection.

00:37:56.830 --> 00:37:58.750 align:middle line:84%
And life, I think,
really is about.

00:37:58.750 --> 00:38:01.180 align:middle line:84%
If you want to have
a fulfilling life,

00:38:01.180 --> 00:38:03.070 align:middle line:84%
you need fulfilling
relationships

00:38:03.070 --> 00:38:07.240 align:middle line:84%
with others, with yourself,
and with your food

00:38:07.240 --> 00:38:09.600 align:middle line:90%
and your environment.

00:38:09.600 --> 00:38:14.000 align:middle line:90%